WEBVTT

00:05.306 --> 00:10.611
* Oh, oh, oh,
 I'm comin' down *

00:10.678 --> 00:15.649
* With a bad case of you

00:15.716 --> 00:18.452
* Please help me, darlin'

00:18.519 --> 00:20.421
- You know what?
- Oh, crazy.

00:20.488 --> 00:23.257
- And then he-- yesterday?
 - Yeah?

00:23.324 --> 00:24.892
He takes me on a hike.

00:24.958 --> 00:25.993
Where, like in the woods?

00:26.060 --> 00:27.695
- Yeah.
- Oh, no. Nuh-uh.

00:27.761 --> 00:29.430
Why would anyone choose
 to go hiking in the woods?

00:29.497 --> 00:31.132
Uch, there's
 rapists out there,

00:31.199 --> 00:32.400
and worse--
 no, no, no, no, worse,

00:32.466 --> 00:34.602
coyotes and I don't know,
bear shit.

00:34.668 --> 00:36.270
Well, it was his idea.

00:36.337 --> 00:37.238
You know,
 he's always coming up

00:37.305 --> 00:38.806
with these little adventures.

00:38.872 --> 00:40.441
I mean, it's so cute.

00:40.508 --> 00:42.510
Yeah, yeah.
 He'd better be cute

00:42.576 --> 00:44.245
if he's going to steal
 you away from me.

00:44.312 --> 00:46.114
Oh, [scoff].
 Oh. Oh, here he is.

00:46.180 --> 00:47.781
I can't wait.
You're going to love him.

00:47.848 --> 00:49.550
- Mm-hmm. I'm sure.
 - Hey. Hi.

00:49.617 --> 00:50.451
Hi.

00:52.253 --> 00:54.522
Sorry
 to keep you waiting.

00:54.588 --> 00:56.757
Morton Pfefferman,
 Shelly Lipkin.

00:56.824 --> 00:58.159
Mort.

00:58.226 --> 00:59.393
Shelly.

01:01.962 --> 01:03.564
Wow. Here I was
 beginning to think

01:03.631 --> 01:06.234
you were entirely imaginary.

01:06.300 --> 01:07.568
- [chuckle]
 - Yeah.

01:07.635 --> 01:10.171
Well, here I am.

01:11.772 --> 01:14.142
That's a-- That's a hell
of a dress, Deb.

01:14.208 --> 01:16.677
Oh, Shelly picked it out.
She's got a good eye.

01:16.744 --> 01:18.045
- Yeah?
 - I do.

01:18.112 --> 01:19.447
I do have a great left eye.

01:19.513 --> 01:20.748
Really strong left eye.

01:20.814 --> 01:21.882
It's good.

01:21.949 --> 01:22.983
* [music gets louder]

01:23.050 --> 01:25.186
[chatter]

01:27.388 --> 01:28.822
[no audible dialogue]

